<div class="my-12">
	<h2 class="font-normal text-blue-950 text-4xl center">
		Get to know TypeGPU
	</h2>
	<p class="text-blue-900 text-2xl text-pretty">
		Dive into guides, tutorials, and videos to see how TypeGPU can change
		the way you work with GPU rendering and computing.
	</p>
</div>

